    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction is accepted. Seven of thirteen credibility factors have been assessed; Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification has been performed on operating-condition inputs; and validation data are available for the primary operating points. The assessment team considers the evaluated factors sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class III VAD device.",
